56
00:02:37,046 --> 00:02:39,696
is if you were to drink it or eat it,

57
00:02:39,696 --> 00:02:43,475
that it would have this kind
of sharp sour taste to it,

58
00:02:43,475 --> 00:02:46,400
while if you go to the
other end of the spectrum,

59
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:49,846
things that are basic, these
would be things like bleaches

