In fact, even soap is quite basic.

64
00:03:01,282 --> 00:03:03,498
And of the basic things
that you could eat,

65
00:03:03,498 --> 00:03:07,755
you might have a bitter
taste associated with it.

66
00:03:07,755 --> 00:03:09,941
But to be clear, I really don't recommend

67
00:03:09,941 --> 00:03:13,494
eating or drinking anything
