68
00:03:13,494 --> 00:03:15,940
or highly acidic, and the reason is

69
00:03:15,940 --> 00:03:19,143
is that things that are at
the extreme of the pH scale,

70
00:03:19,143 --> 00:03:22,233
so things that are either extremely basic

71
00:03:22,233 --> 00:03:25,150
or things that are extremely acidic

72
00:03:26,012 --> 00:03:29,321
like battery acid or hydrochloric acid,

73
00:03:29,321 --> 00:03:32,807
because they're so reactive,
they will damage you.

74
00:03:32,807 --> 00:03:34,940
If you pour it in your
skin, it will damage you.

75
00:03:34,940 --> 00:03:38,200
If you ingest it, it
will damage your cells

76
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:39,917
and it can even kill you.

77
00:03:39,918 --> 00:03:42,507
So don't try to taste things to see

78
