Sea water is pretty
close to being neutral.

90
00:04:11,735 --> 00:04:15,006
Milk is not that far off of being neutral.

91
00:04:15,006 --> 00:04:17,064
Now with that said, in order to read

92
00:04:17,064 --> 00:04:20,004
the pH scale appropriately
