to a pH of eight, that
thing with the pH of four

103
00:04:47,819 --> 00:04:49,819
would be 10, 100, 1,000,

104
00:04:51,862 --> 00:04:53,934
10,000 times more acidic,

105
00:04:53,934 --> 00:04:56,009
or you could say the
thing with a pH of eight

